{"word":"G880 - ἄφωνος - áphōnos - af'-o-nos - Dumb","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἄφωνος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">áphōnos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">af'-o-nos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Dumb</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"சத்தமிடாதிருக்கிற, ஊமையான, பேசாத, அர்த்தமில்லாத - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"voiceless, dumb; without the faculty of speech"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and <a href=\"#/G5456 - φωνή - phōnḗ - fo-nay'/5456\">G5456</a>; <i>voiceless</i>, that is, <i>mute</i> (by nature or choice); figuratively <i>unmeaning:</i> - dumb, without signification.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}